import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='ignore')
    ax = sns.lineplot(x='date', y='price', data=data)
    ax.set(xlabel='Date', ylabel='Price')
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title('What is the overall trend of the S&P 500 index over the given time period?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='daily_return', kde=True)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of daily returns for the S&P 500 index?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Daily Returns')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='ignore')
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='price', data=data)
    std = data['daily_return'].std()
    data['upper'] = data['price'] + std
    data['lower'] = data['price'] - std
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='upper', data=data, color='grey', alpha=0.5)
    sns.lineplot(x='date', y='lower', data=data, color='grey', alpha=0.5)
    plt.fill_between(data['date'], data['upper'], data['lower'], alpha=0.2)
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the volatility of the S&P 500 index over the given time period?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
